title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 20 § 270.2 - Signing of City of Yonkers earnings tax returns and other documents
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 20 § 270.2 - Signing of City of Yonkers earnings tax returns and other documents

State Regulations

Tax Law, § 11 of § 1340(c); Codes and Ordinances of the

City of Yonkers, § 92-108

The provisions of Part 153 of this Title with respect to
the signing of New York State income tax returns, statements and other
documents shall also be applicable to the signing of City of Yonkers earnings
tax returns and other documents. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 20
§
270.2

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
